<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pagina nu a fost găsită | 404</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .error-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50; 
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #c0392b;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background-color: #34495e;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .icon-gavel {
            font-size: 50px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="icon-gavel">⚖️</div>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Obiecție! Pagină respinsă.</h2>
        <p>Se pare că dosarul pe care îl cauți a fost arhivat, mutat sau nu a existat niciodată. Întoarce-te la prima instanță.</p>
        
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">Înapoi la Prima Pagină</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

